<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="tr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Veritabanı bağlantısı - 59 Haber Kutusu</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        *, *::before, *::after { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background: #f5f5f5;
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }
        .card {
            background: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
            padding: 40px 36px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 440px;
        }
        .card h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #B71C1C;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }
        .card p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #424242;
            line-height: 1.65;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .actions {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 12px;
            margin-top: 8px;
        }
        .actions a {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 10px 16px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background 0.2s, color 0.2s;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #D32F2F;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .btn-primary:hover { background: #B71C1C; }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #EEEEEE;
            color: #424242;
        }
        .btn-secondary:hover { background: #E0E0E0; }
        .muted {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #757575;
            margin-top: 24px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1>Veritabanına bağlanılamıyor</h1>
        <p><%= typeof message !== 'undefined' ? message : 'MongoDB bağlantısı kurulamadı.' %></p>
        <div class="actions">
            <a href="javascript:location.reload()" class="btn-primary">Sayfayı yenile</a>
            <a href="/<%= adminPath %>/cikis" class="btn-secondary">Oturumu kapat</a>
            <a href="/" class="btn-secondary">Ana sayfa</a>
        </div>
        <p class="muted">Sunucu konsolunda (Atlas) IP erişim veya bağlantı dizesi hataları detaylı görünür.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
